{"route":"/docs/reference/layout/columns/","title":"Columns","description":"Documentation for the `columns` function.","part":null,"outline":[{"id":"summary","name":"概要","children":[]},{"id":"page-level","name":"ページレベルの段組","children":[]},{"id":"breaking-out","name":"段組の中断","children":[]},{"id":"parameters","name":"引数","children":[{"id":"parameters-count","name":"count","children":[]},{"id":"parameters-gutter","name":"gutter","children":[]},{"id":"parameters-body","name":"body","children":[]}]}],"body":{"kind":"func","content":{"path":[],"name":"columns","title":"Columns","keywords":[],"oneliner":"領域を等幅の複数段に分割。","element":true,"contextual":false,"deprecation":null,"details":"<p>領域を等幅の複数段に分割。</p>\n<p><code>column</code>関数を用いることで、あらゆるコンテナの内部を複数の段に分割することができます。\n現在、段の高さのバランスは取れません。\nその代わり、段はコンテナの高さかページの残りの高さを占めます。\nバランスを取った段組は将来的にサポートされる予定です。</p>\n<h2 id=\"page-level\">ページレベルの段組</h2>\n<p>ドキュメント全体に渡る段組を挿入する必要がある場合は、代わりに<code>page</code>関数の<a href=\"/docs/reference/layout/page/#parameters-columns\"><code>columns</code>パラメーター</a>を使用してください。\nこれは、レイアウトコンテナ内のコンテンツ全てをラップするのではなく、ページレベルの段組を直接作成します。\n結果として<a href=\"/docs/reference/layout/pagebreak/\">改ページ</a>、<a href=\"/docs/reference/model/footnote/\">脚注</a>および<a href=\"/docs/reference/model/par/#definitions-line\">行番号</a>のようなものが期待通りの動作をし続けます。\nより詳しくは<a href=\"/docs/guides/page-setup-guide/#columns\">ページのセットアップガイドの関連する項目</a>をご覧ください。</p>\n<h2 id=\"breaking-out\">段組の中断</h2>\n<p>（例えば、論文のタイトルのように）段組を一時的に中断する場合は、親スコープでのフロート配置を使用してください。</p>\n<div class=\"previewed-code\"><pre><code><span class=\"typ-key\">#</span><span class=\"typ-key\">set</span> <span class=\"typ-func\">page</span><span class=\"typ-punct\">(</span>columns<span class=\"typ-punct\">:</span> <span class=\"typ-num\">2</span><span class=\"typ-punct\">,</span> height<span class=\"typ-punct\">:</span> <span class=\"typ-num\">150pt</span><span class=\"typ-punct\">)</span>\n\n<span class=\"typ-func\">#</span><span class=\"typ-func\">place</span><span class=\"typ-punct\">(</span>\n  top <span class=\"typ-op\">+</span> center<span class=\"typ-punct\">,</span>\n  scope<span class=\"typ-punct\">:</span> <span class=\"typ-str\">&quot;parent&quot;</span><span class=\"typ-punct\">,</span>\n  float<span class=\"typ-punct\">:</span> <span class=\"typ-key\">true</span><span class=\"typ-punct\">,</span>\n  <span class=\"typ-func\">text</span><span class=\"typ-punct\">(</span><span class=\"typ-num\">1.4em</span><span class=\"typ-punct\">,</span> weight<span class=\"typ-punct\">:</span> <span class=\"typ-str\">&quot;bold&quot;</span><span class=\"typ-punct\">)</span><span class=\"typ-punct\">[</span>\n    My document\n  <span class=\"typ-punct\">]</span><span class=\"typ-punct\">,</span>\n<span class=\"typ-punct\">)</span>\n\n<span class=\"typ-func\">#</span><span class=\"typ-func\">lorem</span><span class=\"typ-punct\">(</span><span class=\"typ-num\">40</span><span class=\"typ-punct\">)</span>\n</code></pre><div class=\"preview\"><img src=\"/docs/assets/a8d4661ddb4d82cf2aa44f91511f97c9.png\" alt=\"Preview\"></div></div>","example":null,"self":false,"params":[{"name":"count","details":"<p>段数。</p>","example":null,"types":["int"],"strings":[],"default":"<code><span class=\"typ-num\">2</span></code>","positional":true,"named":false,"required":false,"variadic":false,"settable":true},{"name":"gutter","details":"<p>段間。</p>","example":null,"types":["relative"],"strings":[],"default":"<code><span class=\"typ-num\">4%</span> <span class=\"typ-op\">+</span> <span class=\"typ-num\">0pt</span></code>","positional":false,"named":true,"required":false,"variadic":false,"settable":true},{"name":"body","details":"<p>段内にレイアウトされるべきコンテンツ。</p>","example":null,"types":["content"],"strings":[],"default":null,"positional":true,"named":false,"required":true,"variadic":false,"settable":false}],"returns":["content"],"scope":[]}}}